ed9790fbadfb38e4d660eb1befd87e803d70dec04d936e8cd26def4a9c21240bb7cae8750ae3395aa4761e6738b9e346c86ba57761cfde30efe46d2cb459a7e4  minio.confd
4d3f296b348c177f580ff8e06fcd07a24659c0ddf936593058ebabc31766ba1c80839bd29e27b647982c141861b58206ed9c17e2fbf1fc1099a2775b1926988c  RELEASE.2019-06-01T03-46-14Z.tar.gz"
